org.realityforge.anodoc - package org.realityforge.anodoc
This package contains the anodoc annotations.

T

TestOnly - Annotation Type in org.realityforge.anodoc
Mark an element only exists to be called from testing code.

U

Unsupported - Annotation Type in org.realityforge.anodoc
This annotation is used to mark elements that are unsupported.

V

VisibleForTesting - Annotation Type in org.realityforge.anodoc
Mark an element only is more widely visible so it can be called from testing code.
